wikipedia_page.main: Reginald Thomas Herbert Fletcher, 1st Baron Winster,  (27 March 1885 – 7 June 1961) was a British Liberal then Labour politician. He was Minister of Civil Aviation under Clement Attlee between 1945 and 1946 and Governor of Cyprus between 1946 and 1949.
